column5: Self contained cottage just a few minutes to Zilker Park and downtown. Newly remodeled. Located in the leafy western suburb of Rollingwood, a very short walk to 24hr FedEx Print & Ship Center, USPS, Randall's, Starbucks, Chipotle, and other nearby shops and restaurants. Fenced back yard.
column8: Modern, studio-like 2BR House 1 Mile from downtown
